title: american horror story coven - young fiona kills anna leigh the last supreme 3x3 opening scene
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: I always thought this was a sad scene. She killed the supreme, so she could become the supreme, only to run off and avoid the responsibilities of being a supreme. Basically Anna Leigh died for nothing
The girl acting is good at pretending to be a young Jessica Lange.
God I want Mimi DeLampré’s story so damn bad tho.

I don't know why but I love the moment when Anna Leigh lights her cigarette. It's such a subtle effect of power display but it always makes me more interested in her as a character and the previous supremes.
Coven was and is STILL the best season of AHS
